BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (A Type 2 diabetes diagnosis can feel overwhelming, but it is a condition that responds) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (remarkably well to lifestyle management. Many people achieve excellent blood sugar control) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- and even remission - through nutrition, exercise, and consistent self-monitoring.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (This workbook provides everything you need to track, manage, and improve your blood sugar) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (control with practical tools and evidence-based strategies.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
