BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 3: Blood Sugar Management Strategies) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (The Glucose Equation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Blood sugar is affected by: Food \(raises it\), Exercise \(lowers it\), Medication \(lowers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (it\), Stress \(raises it\), Sleep \(poor sleep raises it\), Illness \(raises it\).) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 612.4 Td (How to Test Blood Sugar) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.4 Td (- Wash hands with warm water \(cold hands give low readings\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.4 Td (- Use side of fingertip \(less painful\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.4 Td (- Rotate fingers and sites) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.4 Td (- Record immediately in your log) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 524.6 Td (When to Test) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 508.6 Td (- Fasting \(first thing in morning\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 494.6 Td (- Before meals) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 480.6 Td (- 2 hours after first bite of meals) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 466.6 Td (- Before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 452.6 Td (- Before and after exercise) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.6 Td (- When feeling 'off' \(high or low symptoms\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 408.8 Td (Recognizing Highs and Lows) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 386.8 Td (High Blood Sugar \(Hyperglycemia\) Signs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 370.8 Td (- Increased thirst and frequent urination) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 356.8 Td (- Blurred vision) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 342.8 Td (- Fatigue and headache) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 328.8 Td (- Slow healing wounds) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 310.8 Td (Low Blood Sugar \(Hypoglycemia\) Signs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 294.8 Td (- Shakiness, sweating, rapid heartbeat) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 280.8 Td (- Dizziness, confusion) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 266.8 Td (- Hunger) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 252.8 Td (- Irritability) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 225.0 Td (Rule of 15 for Low Blood Sugar) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 209.0 Td (- If below 70 mg/dL: Eat 15g fast-acting carbs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 195.0 Td (- Wait 15 minutes and retest) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 181.0 Td (- If still low, repeat) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 167.0 Td (- Once normal, eat a balanced snack) Tj ET
endstream
